<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Nichuahlei Siangpahrang kannih, Pathum nih khual kan tlawn pah in, Lo
 le cerh le fing le tlang ah, Arfi kan zulh lengmang.

[C1]
   Maw, khuaruahharmi zan arfi, Aa dawh ngaingaimi arfi, Nitlaklei ah
   kan hruai lengmang, Na ceunak kan phak hlan tiang.

[V2]
 Bethlehem chuakmi Siangpahrang, Chinh thanawk sui ka rak i put, Dong
 hin loin kan siangpahrang, Kannih kan umpi tuah.

[C2]
   Maw, khuaruahharmi zan arfi, Aa dawh ngaingaimi arfi, Nitlaklei ah
   kan hruai lengmang, Na ceunak kan phak hlan tiang.

[V3]
 Pek dingah frenkensens ka ngei, Pathian biaknak caah zihmui, Mi vialte
 nih an thangthat i, Lianngan Pathian an biak.

[C3]
   Maw, khuaruahharmi zan arfi, Aa dawh ngaingaimi arfi, Nitlaklei ah
   kan hruai lengmang, Na ceunak kan phak hlan tiang.

[V4]
 Cinthling kei ka laksawng a si, Hi zihmui rim a khami hi; Ngaihchiat
 khuaruahhar le thi chuah, Hmelchunhnak cu a si.

[C4]
   Maw, khuaruahharmi zan arfi, Aa dawh ngaingaimi arfi, Nitlaklei ah
   kan hruai lengmang, Na ceunak kan phak hlan tiang.

[V5]
 Zohhmanh, thangthatnak in a tho, Pathian kannih kan Khamhtu cu,
 Hallelujah, Hallelujah, Van le lei ah a thang.

[C5]
   Maw, khuaruahharmi zan arfi, Aa dawh ngaingaimi arfi, Nitlaklei ah
   kan hruai lengmang, Na ceunak kan phak hlan tiang.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>NICHUAHLEI SIANGPAHRANG PATHUM CH93</title>
<hymn_number>93</hymn_number>
</song>